						<h5 class="card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3 display-7">A user-centered approach to <em><strong>creative problem solving</strong></em>, divided into 5 stages: empathize, define, ideate, prototype and test.<br><br>I applied it in the development of an app for a virtual assistant that supports the understanding and care of Alzheimer's, <em><strong>focusing on the emotional and cognitive needs</strong></em> of the users.<br><br></h5>
