						<h4 class="card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0 display-7">
							<strong>SCRUM</strong></h4>
						<h5 class="card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3 display-7">An agile framework for <strong><em>project management that prioritizes collaboration</em></strong>, working in sprints and iterative deliveries of value.<br><br>I used Scrum in collaborative projects such as the Saberes UPB Summer School, where we designed an immersive virtual reality experience, <strong><em>combining design, narrative and technology</em></strong></h5>					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-6">
