						<h4 class="card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0 display-7">
							<strong>Lean UX</strong></h4>
						<h5 class="card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3 display-7">An agile methodology for experience design <em style=""><strong>focused on learning quickly, validating hypotheses and reducing waste</strong></em>through experiments.<br><br><br><div>In a redesign initiative for an educational platform, I used Lean UX to <strong>validate functionalities with rapid prototyping</strong>, improving user interaction and retention.</div></h5>					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="item features-without-image col-12 col-lg-6">
