						<h4 class="card-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0 display-7"><strong>Design Sprint</strong></h4>
						<h5 class="card-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3 display-7">5-day intensive process to solve problems and validate ideas through <strong>design, prototyping, and user testing</strong>. <br><br>I applied Design Sprint in an innovation challenge where in 5 days we <strong>generated, prototyped, and tested</strong> a solution to improve <strong>the learning experience</strong> for illiterate people.</h5>
